OnInit
API Method viperOverlay POST
API Header viperOverlay "Content-Type" "application/json"
API Url viperOverlay http://localhost/viposmk3/_data/update/

OnCommand bm 0 !smack
ManualOverlayUpdates
UpdateViperOverlay

OnAction ManualOverlayUpdates
API GET https://decapi.me/twitch/followers/dr_viper
Variable Set viperFollower {api_data}
API GET https://decapi.me/twitch/latest_sub/dr_viper
Variable Set viperSubscriber {api_data}
API GET https://decapi.me/twitch/subcount/dr_viper
Variable Set viperSubCount {api_data}

OnAction UpdateViperOverlay
Variable Load viperFollower
Variable Load viperSubscriber
Variable Load viperSubCount
Variable Load viperGoal
API RawData viperOverlay "{ \"follower\": \"{viperFollower}\", \"subscriber\": \"{viperSubscriber}\", \"subCount\": \"{viperSubCount}\", \"goal\": \"{viperGoal}\" }"
API Send viperOverlay